{"tid":1133634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入來睇下169尺點樣住到 4個大人 [多圖] 低賤奴性系列","createTime":"2019-05-01T08:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T08:58:58.000Z","uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f4874720252daae4d5cbc566c1b12478e61a43","tid":1133634,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/photos/a.178021259752739/281110226110508/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkopentv%2Fphotos%2Fa.178021259752739%2F281110226110508%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=3b42c028\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/photos/a.178021259752739/281110226110508/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F78GYnJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF78GYnJ.png&h=6ff98ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開番係房屋台先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得登CAP圖俾大家睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全理解唔到香港人低賤奴性既底線係點<br />\n4個大人自住.....<br />\n唔洗計校網...<br />\n你話買樓放租俾單身返工人士就話者.....<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅人口密度愈來愈高，由八十年代嘅微型單位到今日嘅納米樓，到底要點樣住一家大細呢？今集，我哋請嚟高級設計經理葉錦雄Alvin，幫何文田一個三尖八角嘅單位設計出俾四個成年人住嘅空間，不過扣咗兩個露台仔，室內可用面積得169平方呎！Alvin都坦言呢個係佢入行以嚟第一次設計咁細嘅單位，係一個大挑戰！不過大師就係大師，佢將呢個小小嘅生活空間向高空發展，令單位上層可用面積增加110平方呎！成個單位擺得落一張雙人床同兩張單人床之餘，仲有二十幾個儲物櫃，到底Alvin係點樣將呢個細單位變成獨立優質小樓房呢？即刻重溫《立邦淨味兒童漆特約：夠細奇則》啦<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkopentv.com/#/videopage/BW00894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkopentv.com%2F%23%2Fvideopage%2FBW00894&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=d347e770\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkopentv.com/#/videopage/BW00894</a>"},{"pid":"e9bf386d0e79c1384a2e179828b1ec4421f83d90","tid":1133634,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"25c405ddb1929278b6109a4c82fd4419cba92cb2","tid":1133634,"uid":66701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9bf386d0e79c1384a2e179828b1ec4421f83d90","tid":1133634,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"請去番房屋台討論<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1133638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1133638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"603ba6894e0917f3ba7f58ab306da157af5b5799","tid":1133634,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"公屋仔：戶主個仔住私樓都冇私人空間打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公屋又贏"},{"pid":"9b41aa4bb2c7b9de321990c559e7d00711c41562","tid":1133634,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}